1462527666.text: "It has been reported that miR-181b reduces IGF-1R expression in tumor cells, and inhibits VEGF induced PI3K-Akt signaling; 54 in contrast, in T cells it may reduce PTEN expression, thereby promoting PI3K-Akt signaling."
